#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:60
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kmail;'s configuration window enables you to configure &kmail; in many "
#| "ways. You can reach it via <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
